# Treat binary IQ recordings as binary (do not run line-ending or diff transforms)
*.complex16s binary
*.complex     binary
*.cfile       binary
*.iq          binary
*.sigmf-data  binary

# Optional: track via Git LFS (recommended for repositories that will accumulate
# many or larger captures). Enable by installing git-lfs and running:
#   git lfs install
#   git lfs track "*.complex16s"
# After tracking, commit `.gitattributes` and add files normally.
